author: The Critical Drinker
description:
He was hailed as one of the most unique and talented directors of his generation. The man who gave us Jojo Rabbit and Thor Ragnarok, but then it all came crashing down with the disastrous release of Thor Love And Thunder - a movie so bad that it practically destroyed his career. This is the story of Taika Waititi.
